irements needed to run luclin... and already they are killing my sunshine before i can even play    <IMG SRC="frown.gif" border="0"> . well i guess they are happy, since while i wasnt able to even log on the old everquest due to tech issues with the files they sent to my system they were still charging my Visa for this month...I really dont like being a paying beta tester....<P>/sigh<BR>/apologize for the rant<P>Jeregne D'Amour<BR>52nd Norrathian Dictate<BR>Sneaky Snake of Innoruuk<P>-i am gifted in many fields, however at 3am spelling isn't one of them-<P><BR>(edit: sorry Llorian, i didnt see your last post. before i made this one. i do apologize and thank you for testing)
